// The Ledger, chapter 4 of 4: THE BUYER. The finale forks - and the two
// endings DIVERGE, not just in flavor text. Two beacons open the branch
// (OnEnter sets `choice`, gauntlet-style):
//   - SELL (HANDOFF berth): dock the box and the sale calls the hammer down.
//     The AUDITOR gunship ARRIVES (telegraphed: warning line, far spawn, 8s
//     engage_delay grace) and you must break it. Terminal outcome: PAYDAY AT
//     A PRICE (Victory, debt cleared, a gunship was the cost).
//   - BURN (buoy): torch the box and there is nothing left to collect, so the
//     Auditor NEVER comes. NO fight. Terminal outcome: SAFE BUT BROKE
//     (Victory, clear but no payout). This path latches act -> 3 at the buoy
//     and lands its own overlay a beat later; the Auditor is not spawned.
// Branching lives INSIDE the chapter - variables do not survive scenario
// changes (spike 20260716-183104). This is the last chapter: neither ending
// chains to a NextScenario (only the Defeat retry requeues the finale).
//
// Acts: 1 = the choice, 2 = the (sell-only) fight, 3 = done. `choice`:
// 1 = sold, 2 = burned. Player-death Defeat gates act < 3, so it can only
// fire on the sell path (the burn path is already at act 3).
[
    Scenario((
        id: "ledger_ch4_the_buyer",
        name: "The Ledger 4: The Buyer",
        description: "Everyone wants the box. Decide who gets it - then survive the decision. Chapter four of The Ledger.",
        cubemap: "dep://base/textures/cubemap.png",
        thumbnail: Some("dep://base/textures/asteroid.png"),
        hidden: true,
        events: [
            (
                name: OnStart,
                filters: [],
                actions: [
                    VariableSet((
                        key: "act",
                        expression: Term(Factor(Literal(Number(1.0)))),
                    )),
                    VariableSet((
                        key: "choice",
                        expression: Term(Factor(Literal(Number(0.0)))),
                    )),
                    // Burn-ending one-shots: the burn path bumps `act` to 3
                    // synchronously (no death window) and lands its Victory a
                    // beat later on `burn_gate`, guarded once by `burn_said`.
                    // Seeded here so the deferred OnUpdate reads defined values.
                    VariableSet((
                        key: "burn_gate",
                        expression: Term(Factor(Literal(Number(0.0)))),
                    )),
                    VariableSet((
                        key: "burn_said",
                        expression: Term(Factor(Literal(Number(0.0)))),
                    )),
                    StoryMessage((
                        speaker: "Broker Vesh",
                        text: "Here's the arithmetic, Kestrel: my buyer pays enough to clear your debt twice. Or you burn the box and nobody owns what's inside. Berth or buoy. Pick.",
                    )),
                    Objective((
                        id: "obj_ch4_recap",
                        message: "Ch.4 - The Buyer: sell the box (HANDOFF) or destroy it (BURN).",
                    )),
                    SpawnScenarioObject((
